#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
Generic SObject Automation Audit — field metadata + automation analysis for any SObject.

For every field on the target SObject, captures:
  - Full field metadata (type, picklist values, behavior, formula, default, encryption,
    reporting availability, population rate, created/modified dates)
  - Which active Apex Triggers reference the field (read or write)
  - Which active Flows reference the field (entry criteria, read, write)
  - Which Validation Rules reference the field
  - Which Workflow Field Updates target the field
  - Whether the field is SET (written) by any automation

Automation analysis is scoped purely to the target SObject — no cross-object
(Account / Contact / Opportunity) filtering is applied.

Usage:
  python3 scripts/generate_sobject_automation_audit.py <ObjectApiName> <OrgAlias> <OutputExcel>

Examples:
  python3 scripts/generate_sobject_automation_audit.py Account ComdataProd scripts/Account_Automation_Audit.xlsx
  python3 scripts/generate_sobject_automation_audit.py MultiCard_Setup__c ComdataProd scripts/MultiCard_Audit.xlsx

Output: Excel file with one sheet containing all fields + automation details.
Cache:  /tmp/soauto_<OrgAlias>_<ObjectApiName>/ — delete to force refresh.
"""

